----------------------------
copyem              : Copies the relavant sizes to the android labyrynth.
distans-icon.odp    : Icon in Presentation 512x512
distans-icon.png    : Exported png to go to ../src/assets/images and uploaded to https://www.appicon.co/#image-sets to get ~/Downloads/ImageSets.zip
distans-splash.odp  : Splash in Presentation 1080x1920
distans-splash.png  : Exported png uploaded to https://www.appicon.co/#image-sets to get ~/Downloads/ImageSets.zip
Icons.zip           : mv ~/Downloads/ImageSets.zip ./Icons.zip
Splash.zip          : mv ~/Downloads/ImageSets.zip ./Splash.zip

1) Create splash (1080x1920) and icon (512x512) in LibreOffice Presentation (get aspect ratio right in cm)
2) Export as distans-[icon|splash].png - splash 1080x1920 and icon 512x512
3) Copy distans-icon.png to ../src/assets/images for display in header etc.
4) Upload distans-icon.png to https://www.appicon.co/#image-sets (4x) and get ~/Downloads/ImageSets.zip
5) mv ~/Downloads/ImageSets.zip ./Icons.zip
6) Upload distans-splash.png to https://www.appicon.co/#image-sets (4x) and get ~/Downloads/ImageSets.zip
7) mv ~/Downloads/ImageSets.zip ./Splash.zip
8) unzip Icons.zip; unzip Splash.zip
9) . ./copyem

