Android Studio - Build etc.


Release Build etc :
% keytool -genkeypair -v -storetype PKCS12 -keystore scremblev2.keystore -alias scremblv2-alias -keyalg RSA -keysize 2048 -validity 10000
Then do it via Android Studio : Build -> Generate Signed Bundle or APK -> Android App Bundle -> Next ->
	Key Store Path     : Full path outside this project
	Key Store Password : As entered above
	Key Alias          : scremblv2-alias
	Key Password       : As entered above for want of anything else
	Remember passwords and Export key select
	-> Next -> release -> create
